The NGO XYZ is being funded by a German funding agency for over ten years. But, the NGO did not have a separate budget for this activity. 
a)	As a program officer assigned to be in charge of this activity in the NGO XYZ, please write introduction to a proposal for undertaking this as a special activity to be approved by your superior (CEO of NGO XYZ). Prepare the narrative of the introduction to the proposal along the following outlines given below: 
